[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "「光星隊」……あの隊は、そう名付けられたんだね。\nうん、希望を感じさせるいい名前だ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00112",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "でしょ？　私が名付けたんだ。\nそして……隊長は私！　立候補して選ばれたの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00113",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "頂獣や極夜の錬金党のような脅威に対抗するための\n特殊部隊として、これから頑張っていくよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00114",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "隊員はみんな、私が見定めた精鋭揃いだからね！\nといっても初陣はまだ先だから、当分は訓練漬けかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00115",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "クレオはウェルテックスが来た時、刺激された魔物を\n南部の辺境で完全に抑え込んだ――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00116",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "その定評もあって、特殊部隊の指揮官か。\nさすがじゃないか！　おめでとう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00117",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "へへん、それほどでも……あるけど？\nもっとほめてほめて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00118",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "よっ！　闘う王女様！　自慢の妹！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00119",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私はこれからより責任のある立場になる。\n部下だけじゃない、国民みんなの命が懸かってるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00120",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そんな期待と責任を背負えるだけの力はある……\n私自身、そう思ってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00121",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "白夜の騎士、ユナにはかなわないかもだけど……\nううん、ユナにだって、いつか勝ってみせるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00122",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "うん、その意気だ。クレオみたいな勇気ある者が\n隊長なら、光星隊はきっといい隊になるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_037_00123",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん！　私についてきてくれる部下たちのためにも、\n隊長として精一杯頑張るよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00124",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "みんな、討伐訓練お疲れさま！　いい連携だったよ！\n王女より「素晴らしい成果で賞」を授与します！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00125",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "光星隊員Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "光栄です！　でも上手くいったのは\n隊長の的確な指示があってこそですよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_721_037_00126",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "光星隊員Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "隊としても、俺自身も、成長を感じています。\n隊長のご指導ご鞭撻のおかげです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_722_037_00127",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私もみんなの隊長として鼻が高いよ～！\nみんな、私についてきてくれてありがとう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00128",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "さぁ、光星隊！　この調子で訓練を重ねて、\n初陣を華々しく飾ってあげましょーっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00129",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "光星隊員Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なんだ、この強さ……！\nこれまでの魔物の、比じゃない……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_721_037_00130",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "光星隊員Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺たちの連携が通じない……！\nすべて、見抜かれてるみたいだ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_722_037_00131",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "１班！　２班！　みんな！\nそ、そんな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00132",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あなたたち……いったい、何者……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00133",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺か？　名乗る謂れはないが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00134",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私はクレオ・ランターナ。\nランターナ王女にして、光星隊の隊長よ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00135",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ほう。俺はヘルト。九偉人の長兄にして、\nこの世界の英雄だ。こっちはゼロ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00136",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "今の世界を見て回るついでに「王国の精鋭部隊」が\nいると聞いたんで寄ってみたんじゃが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00137",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "この程度で精鋭とは。俺たちが寝ている間も\n人類はまったく進歩していなかったらしい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00138",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ヘルト……ゼロ……！\nよくも……よくも私の大切な部下たちを……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00139",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "言っておくが、誰一人殺してないぞ。\n力を量るためだけの遊びだからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00140",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "とはいえ、何人かは深手じゃ。\nさっさと手当てしてやるんじゃな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00141",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ではな、「こうえいたい」とやら。\n二度と会うことはないだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00142",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "「こうえいたい」じゃない……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00143",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "「光星隊」だ……！　これから、華々しく……！！\nランターナの平和を守る……特殊部隊だ……！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00144",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ヘルトにゼロ……覚えた……！！\n部下たちの借りは、私が必ず……！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00145",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]